14:28.165 --> 14:55.135
immediately put in charge of taking care of the 
funding for the contracts for Woods Hole and

14:28.165 --> 14:55.135
Scripps Institution of Oceanography, working 
under Meredith D. Williams, Dick Williams.

14:57.916 --> 15:12.397
and Ned Shearer, who were in that department, 
